Package csc555.ebratt.depaul.edu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GroupByCountPair
    GroupByCountPair is a class that allows for secondary sorting in a hadoop framework.
    GroupByCountPairPartitioner
    GroupByCountPairPartitioner is a custom partitioner used in a hadoop job to ensure that GroupByCountPair objects are sent to the same reducer based on their groupBy values.
    GroupByGroupingComparator
    GroupByGroupingComparator is a custom comparator used in a hadoop job to ensure that GroupByCountPair objects are grouped using their groupBy fields.
    PutMerge
    PutMerge is a class that takes multiple files on a local filesystem and puts them on HDFS in a merged file.
    RCTop10Driver
    RCTop10Driver is the hadoop class that drives the program.
    RCTop10Driver.RCTop10Mapper
    RCTop10Mapper is the hadoop class that maps the input.
    RCTop10Driver.RCTop10Reducer
    RCTop10Reducer is the hadoop class that reduces the output of the RCTop10Mapper.
    RCWordCountDriver
    RCWordCountDriver is the hadoop class that drives the program.
    RCWordCountDriver.RCWordCountMapper
    RCWordCountMapper is the hadoop class that maps the input.
    RCWordCountDriver.RCWordCountReducer
    RCWordCountReducer is the hadoop class that reduces the output of the RCWordCountMapper.
